{"word":"G4181 - πολυμερῶς - polymerōs - pol-oo-mer'-oce - At sundry times","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πολυμερῶς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">polymerōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pol-oo-mer'-oce</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">At sundry times</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பங்குபங்காக - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"by many portions"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from a compound of <a href=\"#/G4183 - πολύς - polýs - pol-oos'/4183\">G4183</a> and <a href=\"#/G3313 - μέρος - méros - mer'-os/3313\">G3313</a>; <i>in many portions</i>, that is, <i>variously</i> as to time and agency (<i>piecemeal</i>): - at sundry times.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4178/4178\">G4178</a>, <a href=\"#/G4180/4180\">G4180</a>, <a href=\"#/G4181/4181\">G4181</a>, <a href=\"#/G4182/4182\">G4182</a>, <a href=\"#/G4183/4183\">G4183</a>"}]}